019-07-22T00:48:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">元朗南邊圍村<br />\n禍必及妻兒<br />\n近排乾燥<br />\n小心火警<br />\n何君堯老母 <br />\n良田村青山基督教墳場 <br />\n李趣寬<br />\n千奇唔好起佢老母山墳<br />\n唔好推到見到墳頭相<br />\n</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:34:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dbe79d657d7430951427810aea102323a219aa81","tid":1344841,"uid":39568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:34:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/2599196560114478/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F223783954322429%2Fposts%2F2599196560114478%2F&d=D9%2BIkncl4BF5lZ8wPV9kyFLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=aca714a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/2599196560114478/</a><br />\n前者針對政權，後者針對平民，政府新聞處居然將兩者混為一談，這是徹頭徹尾的偷換概念。<br />\n<br />\n元朗發生的事，屬於 (1) 無差別襲擊，完全針對平民；(2) 遇襲者完全沒有攻擊性，包括老弱婦孺；(3) 維持時間長達數小時，屬連續、反覆出現的攻擊；(4) 目的是製造公眾無論在任何地方都對個人安全產生的恐慌。上環，(1)-(4) 都沒有出現。<br />\n<br />\n假如元朗案在世界任何其他地方出現，定義上，這都是一場Terrorist Attack，領袖會定性，嚴查，做一切可做的穩定人心。<br />\n<br />\n政府、警方，卻將之與政治事件混淆；處理元朗的態度，僅視之為有人受傷的私人糾紛。<br />\n<br />\n沒有想過認識的政府中人，會變得這樣。"},{"pid":"ae14fe165487d1f6b6815e4f12bfe127c945af98","tid":1344841,"uid":243407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:35:36.000Z","msg":"一陣要去入油<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d204796d290c67c4a3507e56550dc1c91ba595c0","tid":1344841,"uid":243407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae14fe165487d1f6b6815e4f12bfe127c945af98","tid":1344841,"uid":243407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:35:36.000Z","msg":"一陣要去入油<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:35:53.000Z","msg":"回錯 對唔住"},{"pid":"699228da38312f